---
title: Carb Smart Wonton-Inspired Beef Meatballs with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This Chinese-inspired dish offers all the delicious flavours of dumplings, but without the wrapper. Minced green onion adds layers of juiciness to the ground beef mix, while fragrant ginger, zucchini, snap peas and mushrooms tie the dish together.

